---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Commercial Umbrella Insurance | Excess Liability | PCFG Insurance" description="Get extra liability protection with commercial umbrella insurance from PCFG. Coverage limits from $1M to $5M+. Protect your business assets. Free quote." keywords="commercial umbrella insurance, excess liability insurance, umbrella coverage, business umbrella policy">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 via-navy-800 to-navy-700 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Commercial Umbrella Insurance</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-8">Extra Protection When It Matters Most</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8">
          Your <span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">$1 million</span> liability policy seemed like enough—until the <span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">$2.3 million</span> judgment.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/commercial-quote" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
            Get an Umbrella Quote
          </a>
          <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
            Call (877) 717-7234
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- The Problem Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Your Standard Limits Aren't Enough</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          A delivery van driver ran a red light and caused a multi-vehicle accident. Three people were seriously injured. Medical bills exceeded $1.8 million. The business's commercial auto policy had a $1 million limit.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700">The gap: $800,000+</p>
          <p class="text-xl text-red-600 mt-2">The business owner had to pay out of pocket—losing their building and nearly everything.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Lawsuit awards are climbing every year. What seemed like adequate coverage five years ago is dangerously low today.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Statistics Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Current Liability Reality</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">$75K-$150K</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">average personal injury settlement</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">$500K-$2M+</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">serious injury cases</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">$5M+</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">catastrophic injury claims</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">$1M</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">your standard policy limit</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- How It Works Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">How Commercial Umbrella Insurance Works</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-800 mb-6 text-center">Example: Serious Injury Claim</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-400 mb-2">1</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Claim Amount</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">$1,500,000</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Serious injury judgment</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-400 mb-2">2</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Primary Policy</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">$1,000,000</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">General liability pays first</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-400 mb-2">3</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Umbrella Kicks In</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">$500,000</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Remaining amount covered</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-6">
          <p class="text-xl text-navy-800 font-semibold">Your out-of-pocket cost: $0 (minus deductible)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Covered By Umbrella -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-6">What Umbrella Covers</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">General Liability Overages</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Slip-and-falls, product liability, property damage, libel/slander</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Commercial Auto Overages</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Serious accidents, multi-vehicle collisions, pedestrian injuries</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Employers Liability</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Employee injury claims, third-party lawsuits, loss of consortium</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Coverage Limits -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-6">Coverage Limits Available</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600">$1M</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">umbrella</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600">$2M</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">umbrella</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600">$3M</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">umbrella</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600">$5M+</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">umbrella</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 text-center">One umbrella policy covers multiple underlying policies</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Who Needs It -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">Who Needs Commercial Umbrella Insurance?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <strong>Every business with assets to protect should consider umbrella coverage.</strong>
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🚗</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-2">Vehicle Fleets</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Delivery services, contractors, logistics companies, sales teams</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🏪</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-2">High Traffic Businesses</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Retail stores, restaurants, hotels, entertainment venues</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">⚠️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-2">Higher Risk Operations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Manufacturing, construction, warehousing, recreation facilities</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🏢</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-2">Asset-Rich Companies</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Real estate holdings, expensive equipment, substantial cash reserves</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">💼</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-2">High Net Worth Owners</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Professional practices, family businesses, investment-backed companies</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">✅</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-2">Every Business</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Any business that wants to protect against catastrophic loss</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Cost Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">Surprisingly Affordable Protection</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">Commercial umbrella premiums are affordable because claims exceeding underlying limits are relatively rare.</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3">
            <span class="text-gray-700">$1 Million Umbrella (low risk)</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-navy-600">$400 - $800/year</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3">
            <span class="text-gray-700">$1 Million Umbrella (moderate risk)</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-navy-600">$800 - $1,500/year</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3">
            <span class="text-gray-700">$1 Million Umbrella (higher risk)</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-navy-600">$1,500 - $3,000/year</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-gray-700">One claim without umbrella</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-red-600">$500K - $2M+</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4">
          <p class="text-green-800 font-semibold">$1 million in additional coverage can cost less than $100/month.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-navy-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Don't Let One Claim Exceed Your Coverage</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8">
        Your standard policies have limits. Serious claims don't. Protect everything you've built with commercial umbrella insurance.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/commercial-quote" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
          Get an Umbrella Quote
        </a>
        <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
          Call (877) 717-7234
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
